{"tid":137781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國經濟放緩　企業去年破產宗數急升54%","createTime":"2017-02-28T05:44:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T17:44:36.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"429e58b7accef2fb8402516e45642af03fd74e94","tid":137781,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T05:44:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170228/bkn-20170228015939647-0228_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170228%2Fbkn-20170228015939647-0228_00842_001.html&d=W0WGn%2FLYmVT4dQ5oB2FXDf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=79afbbed\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170228/bkn-20170228015939647-0228_00842_001.html</a><br />\n02月28日(二) 01:59<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170228/photo/bkn-20170228015939647-0228_00842_001_01p.jpg?20170228090217\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170228%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170228015939647-0228_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20170228090217&h=1c33a193&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（中新社圖片）<br />\n據外國傳媒報道，由於中國政府矢志解決「殭屍企業」債務問題及減少行業產能過剩，令去年中國企業破產宗數急升。<br />\n<br />\n數據顯示，中國法院去年合共處理5,665宗企業破產案例，按年急飆54%，當中約3,600宗已完成，85%企業需要清盤，逾1,600宗案例來自浙江及江蘇省，來自遼寧省的亦有346宗。值得留意的是，遼寧省名義經濟增長去年大跌23%，而整個東三省經濟亦拖累了全國，主因是重工業式微，因而導致企業破產案例上升。<br />\n<br />\n統計數據顯示，中國有大約2,041家「殭屍企業」，合共擁有資產高達3.1萬億元人民幣，若不再處理相關問題，將成為阻礙經濟增長的「炸彈」。"},{"pid":"06f9f409867942046f255eb1c15e209a9313269e","tid":137781,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T05:47:47.000Z","msg":"2015年大陸FDI首次負數，又拋售美國國債令自己再唔係美國最大債主，再加上近期嚴厲監管資金防止外流，再再再加上習總講左棄保GDP求穩定增長，反映支爆味甚濃"},{"pid":"3ee555055887a1e15c034d278a60e28adce460c0","tid":137781,"uid":1882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T05:49:00.000Z","msg":"54<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，呢啲數字得中國做到"},{"pid":"d364c35d484c4f86f1ae31e2cd57ab5572643e1e","tid":137781,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T05:59:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>54<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，呢啲數字得中國做到</blockquote><br />\n全部都一窩峰咁做,爆果陣梗係一窩峰爆"},{"pid":"256fcfc16506adc95c07aedc9cb5bc1a4b90be09","tid":137781,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T06:33:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f098f82d9e98d0090ec7ba68adb01969349ca956","tid":137781,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T06:37:21.000Z","msg":"企業破產，工人失業，罪案率上升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a951306ac8c05aa807c67209d6ae051371231e7","tid":137781,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T06:39:20.000Z","msg":"支那會話係經濟轉型&quot;陣痛&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf1e3bd9c2f818a31cc24ac01dabe1e689c41611","tid":137781,"uid":82720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T06:43:45.000Z","msg":"清除毒瘤之後就係美好明天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"229989f94428641896c08f723d2d37919d753a87","tid":137781,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T13:25:59.000Z","msg":"一定係搵夠退休啦<br />\n支那人咁有錢"},{"pid":"100c101bf44b2e867fff899fa18d60359f7412b7","tid":137781,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T14:08:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1652ba0fa8e2da7f638c2e9056a2ef82e6052f65","tid":137781,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T14:15:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" clas